    "getting_started": {
      "enabled": true,
      "prerequisites": [
        {
          "name": "Node.js",
          "command": "npm install npm@latest -g"
        },
        {
          "name": "Pre-commit",
          "command": "npm install -g pre-commit"
        }
      ],
      "installation_steps": [
        {
          "text": "Add this to your `.pre-commit-config.yaml`:",
          "command": "repos:\n     - repo: https://github.com/actuarysailor/pre-commit-readme-generator\n       rev: v1.0.0  # Use the ref you want to point at\n       hooks:\n         - id: readme-generator-test",
          "language": "yaml"
        },
        {
          "text": "Clone the repo (if contributing)",
          "command": "git clone https://github.com/actuarysailor/pre-commit-readme-generator.git"
        },
        {
          "text": "Install NPM packages",
          "command": "npm install"
        },
        {
          "text": "Create your configuration file",
          "command": "{\n     \"project\": {\n       \"title\": \"Your Project Name\",\n       \"description\": \"Your project description\"\n     }\n   }",
          "language": "json"
        },
        {
          "text": "Generate your README",
          "command": "node src/generator.js your-config.json README.md templates/default.hbs"
        }
      ]
    },
    "usage": {
      "enabled": true,
      "content": "Add the hook to your `.pre-commit-config.yaml`:\n\n```yaml\nrepos:\n  - repo: https://github.com/actuarysailor/pre-commit-readme-generator\n    rev: v1.0.0  # Use the ref you want to point at\n    hooks:\n      - id: readme-generator-test\n```\n\n### Available Hooks\n\n- **`readme-generator-test`**: Validates that your `README.md` matches the\noutput generated from your template and configuration\n- **`readme-generator-update`**: Automatically updates your `README.md` when\ntemplate or config files change\n\n### Repository Structure\n\nYour repository should have:\n\n- `BLANK_README.md` - Handlebars template\n- `configs/example.json` - Configuration file  \n- `README.md` - Generated output\n\nThe hook will validate that `README.md` matches what would be generated from the\ntemplate and config."
    },
